# Keep Vercel from installing the scraper's heavy deps (playwright, lxml) into
# the API serverless function. The root requirements.txt exists only for Railway
# (which runs scraper/main.py from the repo root); Vercel's API function gets its
# deps from api/requirements.txt instead. Railway does not read .vercelignore.
/requirements.txt

# Scraper code is never part of the Vercel build (it runs on Railway).
/scraper
